{"tid":2499725,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Xbox 宣布解除免費線上多人遊戲遊玩限制 今後不需要金會員即可盡情暢玩","createTime":"2021-04-22T06:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T06:28:49.000Z","uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a46b1cf44270aa682e503469913b225738a84476","tid":2499725,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"　　Xbox 宣布，自 4 月 21 日起，所有 Xbox 玩家不需要具備 Xbox Live 金會員資格就可以遊玩免費線上多人遊戲。開放遊玩的遊戲庫中包含超過 50 款免費遊玩的遊戲以及支援線上多人的免費遊戲試玩版和搶鮮版。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd2GwQMv2f6FaKxp6zPtPWssXmvMUp9k354WHms2aN2Yo?filename=0BDjHuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BDjHuV.jpg&h=06b7ad30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　本次開放的對象是免費遊玩、基本遊玩免費或 MMO 類型的遊戲，像是《APEX 英雄》、《要塞英雄》、《戰甲神兵》、《天命 2》、《戰車世界》、《決勝時刻：現代戰域》、《TERA》、《超能競地》等。<br />\n <br />\nXbox 免費遊玩遊戲庫：<a href=\"https://www.xbox.com/zh-hk/games/free-to-play\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fgames%2Ffree-to-play&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=a7b28ba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.xbox.com/zh-hk/games/free-to-play</a><br />\n <br />\n　　此外，為了方便所有玩家彼此搜尋和連絡，微軟將解鎖另外兩個 Xbox Live 金會員的功能「尋找團體」和「派對」，適用於所有 Xbox Series X|S 和 Xbox One 主機。以上變更將自動生效，不需要玩家額外設定。"},{"pid":"700efc5d031ff66fd822feef527d380fefceba1b","tid":2499725,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"德政 追殺PS+<br />\n等睇SONY 跟風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc4ef87575d4e4dda3676e7be0080081ed3d6fd","tid":2499725,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"ps幾時跟機呀 屌佢老母個plus又貴又廢"},{"pid":"3224888cde526fbf97d7b26e747d05583c3618b7","tid":2499725,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700efc5d031ff66fd822feef527d380fefceba1b","tid":2499725,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy